summary: This is a list of kings who ruled over the German territories of central Europe.
full_text: This is a list of monarchs who ruled over the German territories of central Europe from the division of the Frankish Empire in 843 , until the end of the Imperial Germany in 1918. It also includes the heads of the various German confederations after the collapse of the Holy Roman Empire of the German Nation in 1806.
title: List of German monarchs
